import React from 'react'
import SpotifyForm from './components/SpotifyForm';
import { Col, Row, Jumbotron, Container, Display } from 'react-bootstrap';
export const Home = () => (
            <React.Fragment>
                <Row>
                    <Jumbotron>
                        <Container>
                            <Display>test</Display>
                        </Container>
                    </Jumbotron>
                </Row>
                <Row>
                    <Col>
                        <SpotifyForm></SpotifyForm>
                    </Col>
                </Row>
            </React.Fragment>
)
